          "value": "Demographic characteristics [sex, age, body mass index (BMI)], specific comorbidities such as hypertension, diabetes and Parkinson's disease according to current medical history and medications, (CIRS-G) score, treatments with an emphasis on hypotensive drugs. Blood pressure, heart rate. Orthostatic hypotension"
